category: A PROVERBIAL MESS
category comment: (Ken: Please rearrange the mess we made in each of these clues into the correct proverb.)

clue: Son father like like

response: like father like son

clue: Words louder than actions speak

response: actions speak louder than words

clue: From a blood stone you get can't

response: you can't get blood from a stone

clue: Bright on the always side look

response: always look on the bright side

clue: Never better than late

response: better late than never

